   <Ritual>
      <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
         <ab>Y63.4 (mss. 40, 88 (marg.), 400, 410):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            <em>yeŋ́hē.mē aṣ̌āt̰ hacā vahištəm frāgām</em> pad ǰīw bē kunišn pad vaṇtā az dast ī dašn pad datuš barišn pas zōhr abar nihišn tā ō ī  <em>bāgəm aibī.barištəm</em> </ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "(At) <em>yeŋ́hē.mē aṣ̌āt̰ hacā vahištəm</em>, he has to dip the <em>frāgām</em> in the <em>ǰīw</em> and at <em>vaṇtā</em> he has to bring it to the <em>datuš</em> from
            the right hand. Then he has to put <em>zōhr</em> on (the datuš) (and continue) until <em>bāgəm aibī.barištəm</em>."</ab>
      </Nerangs>
   </Ritual>
